In [23]:
png("susie_comparison/ROC_0622_F1.png", 6, 6, units = 'in', res = 500)
plot(d1$susie$true_disc ~ d1$susie$false_disc, t="l", 
     col=colors[1], ylab = "True discoveries", xlab ="False discoveries",
     xlim = c(0,170), ylim = c(0,550))
lines(d2$susie$true_disc ~ d2$susie$false_disc,col=colors[2])
lines(d1$dap$true_disc ~ d1$dap$false_disc,col=colors[3])
legend("bottomright", legend=c("SuSiE (est_var)", "SuSiE (var(Y)))", "DAP-G"),
       col=colors[1:3], lty=c(1,1,1), cex=0.8)
dev.off()
